-- Lumena Resources Plans to Buy Sino Polymer New Materials for $1.4 Billion
-- B y   R i c h a r d   F r o s t
-- 2010-11-07T12:15:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-07/lumena-resources-plans-to-buy-sino-polymer-new-materials-for-1-4-billion.html
Lumena Resources Corp. said it
entered into an agreement to buy as much as 95 percent of Sino
Polymer New Materials Co. from its shareholders for HK$11.05
billion. The target company is a PPS resin producer, Lumena said
in a statement to the Hong Kong stock exchange, saying its
shares will resume trading tomorrow.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Richard Frost at 
 rfrost4@bloomberg.net  